title: Barcelona mayor at roundtable meeting
description:
(5 Oct 2017) Barcelona Mayor Ada Colau met Thursday with embassy representatives and consuls amid a political crisis following a disputed Catalan independence referendum.
Spain's Constitutional Court has ordered the temporary suspension of a special session of Catalonia's parliament next week where regional officials are expected to possibly vote on breaking away from Spain.
